OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of abduction
OL,4,Cas police search for missing 14-year-
OL,5,Cold
OL,7,FA 60-year-old man and 26-year-old
OL,8,Fwoman have been arrested on suspicion
OL,9,Fof abduction as searches continue to
OL,10,Ffind a missing girl from Rotherham.
OL,12,FCassidy, who is 14 years old, was last
OL,13,Fseen on CCTV in Bridgegate in
OL,14,FRotherham town centre at 7.11pm on
OL,15,FSunday, 29 March.
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police confirmed on
OL,18,FTuesday, 31 March, that a 60-year-old
OL,19,Fman and a 26-year-old woman have been
OL,20,Farrested on suspicion of abduction and
OL,21,Fremain in police custody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
