FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1774973461
OL,3,CTwo arrested on suspicion of abduction
OL,4,Cas police search for missing 14-year-
OL,5,Cold
OL,7,FOfficers have carried out numerous
OL,8,Fenquiries including CCTV trawls, house-
OL,9,Fto-house visits and searches of the
OL,10,Flocal area, while also examining phone
OL,11,Frecords.
OL,13,FCassidy is white, 5ft 4ins tall, with
OL,14,Fvery long ginger hair in a ponytail.
OL,15,FShe was last seen wearing a grey
OL,16,Fhoodie, black leggings and carrying a
OL,17,Fsmall handbag but it's believed she
OL,18,Fmay have changed clothes.
OL,20,FCassidy is known to frequent the
OL,21,FThurcroft area and Clifton Park.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
